'''Ten-star household''' (十星級文明家庭) is a status awarded to [[household]]s in [[Rural society in China|rural China]] that exemplify all of the virtues of modern Chinese [[society]]. In some regions, this brings with it free [[utilities]], [[healthcare]], [[education]], and even [[groceries]].

